snippet.title: EA's STAR WARS Trailer (E3 2016)
snippet.description:
EA's Star Wars E3 2016 Trailer
Subscribe for New Trailers: http://goo.gl/KKBrix 
Visit: http://www.fabianpohl.com

Take a look at what’s going on with some of the amazing Star Wars projects our teams at EA are working on now, including DICE, BioWare, Motive, Visceral Games, Capital Games and our partners at Respawn Entertainment. These experiences will explore different Star Wars eras in different gaming genres on different platforms. 

Subscribe to FabianPohl Trailers to catch up with the latest HD official movie trailer & gameplay trailers in 2016! 

Endcard Links: 
Battlefield 1 Trailer: https://youtu.be/MRleJs4m6bk
Finding Dory Trailer: https://youtu.be/p7phc7lA7M0
